The placeholder value `} else if (min > 0) {` starts with `}`, which closes the if block. So whatever is in the if block body comes BEFORE this placeholder on previous lines. But the problem shows the full file with `<PLACEHOLDER>` as a single marker replacing one line.

Let me count the lines in the shown code more carefully:

```javascript
